<plot>Illuminates the inter-connection between water and every form of life on Earth. Targeting tweens, teens and families, PLANET H2O introduces the complex issues surrounding the world's most vital resource - its water supply - and highlights inspiring stories of conservation, technological intervention and sustainable solutions. Hosted by teen actors America Ferrra and Sara Paxton, two magazine-style episodes, "Water Cycle" and "Watersheds," underscore the need for clean, sustainable sources of water worldwide.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?434649</url></doc>
